text.tspan: Change in onshore wind cost per kilowatt-hour, 1983 to 2017
The levelized cost of electricity (LCOE) from onshore wind, given in 2016 USD per kilowatt-hour (kWh). This is
given as the annual weighted average across in the world, in addition to select countries where data is available.
